      <title>美国核心 CPI 连续第四个月上涨 0.3%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-11/us-core-cpi-increases-0-3-for-fourth-straight-month-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国消费者物价在 11 月份继续上涨，所谓的核心消费者物价指数连续第四个月上涨 0.3%，较去年同期上涨 3.3%。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-11/us-core-cpi-increases-0-3-for-fourth-straight-month-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 13:53:13 GMT</pubDate>
