      <title>风力微弱推动天然气发电，欧洲电力价格突破 1,000 欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/german-intraday-power-prices-jump-on-low-wind-and-higher-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于风力发电量下降导致燃气发电量激增，欧洲电价跃升至每兆瓦时 1,000 欧元以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/german-intraday-power-prices-jump-on-low-wind-and-higher-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 09:53:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行警告称，股市低估通胀回归风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/inflation-reading-matters-more-than-the-equity-market-is-showing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[虽然抗通胀的斗争可能基本取得了胜利，但价格压力带来的紧张局势仍可能破坏人们对降息的信心。股市似乎对这些警告视而不见。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/inflation-reading-matters-more-than-the-equity-market-is-showing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 08:13:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>稳定币发行商 Circle 与币安携手扩大发行范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/stablecoin-issuer-circle-expands-crypto-offering-with-binance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[稳定币 USDC 的发行商 Circle Internet Financial Ltd. 和加密货币交易所币安表示，作为加速增长计划的一部分，他们正在合作扩大该代币在交易平台上的使用。]]></description>
